The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically with color information extraction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of binary descriptors, which could be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the proposed method for making binary descriptors color sensitive could also be relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
